This Privacy Policy explains how our app collects, uses, stores, and protects your personal and financial information.
</string>

    <string name="info_collect">
1. Information We Collect
We collect only the information necessary to provide a smooth and secure experience:
• Personal details such as name, email address, and contact information
• Financial data including income, expenses, and savings
• Transaction data via banking APIs (with user consent)
• App usage data to improve performance
</string>

    <string name="data_use">
2. How We Use Your Information
• Track income, expenses, and savings
• Generate charts and financial insights
• Monitor budgets and send alerts
• Provide investment recommendations
• Improve app performance and security
</string>

    <string name="data_security">
3. Data Security
We use industry-standard security measures. All sensitive data is encrypted and processed securely.
</string>

    <string name="permissions">
4. Data Sharing
We do not sell your data. It is shared only with trusted services or when required by law.
</string>

    <string name="user_control">
5. User Control &amp; Consent
You can review, update, or delete your data anytime and manage permissions.
</string>

    <string name="updates">
6. Policy Updates
We may update this policy. Continued use means acceptance.
</string>
